Pick up the brown bowl with fork inside from the table
Turn around and walk straight and face the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and place the bowl with fork inside, let chill then remove the bowl and close the door
Turn around and walk straight to the table and face it
Place the bowl with fork inside down on the the table
Move to the right slightly so that you are facing the center of the wooden table.
Pick up the bowl containing a fork located between the knife and the tomato from the table.
Turn around and move to the gray refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator door, place the bowl containing a fork on the top right shelf, allow the bowl and fork to cool, then open the refrigerator, pick up the bowl and fork, and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn around, move past the green door, and face the wooden table in the corner of the room.
Place the bowl containing the fork on the edge of the table to the right of the brown egg and in front of the knife.
